             so that cxinc is exposed (as cpp) only to List::Util
             (well, any extension) (well, anyone who does -DPERL_EXT),
             no need to export it globally.
     Branch: perl
	  !> embed.fnc embed.h ext/List/Util/Makefile.PL global.sym
